sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(React)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>Backend
    participant QE as Query<br/>Expander
    participant MeSH as MeSH DB<br/>(DuckDB)
    participant MV as Milvus<br/>(Hybrid Search)
    participant RR as Reranker<br/>(Cross-Encoder)
    participant LLM as LLM<br/>(GPT-4o-mini)
    participant GR as Output<br/>Guardrails
    participant LF as LangFuse

    Note over User,FE: Multimodal Input (text / voice / image / document)

    alt Voice / Image / Document input
        User->>FE: Upload file
        FE->>API: POST /transcribe
        API-->>FE: Transcribed text
        FE-->>User: Review & edit text
    end

    User->>FE: Submit query
    FE->>API: POST /ask (stream: true)

    rect rgb(40, 40, 60)
        Note over API,GR: RAG Pipeline

        API->>QE: Expand query
        QE->>LLM: Extract keywords
        LLM-->>QE: Keywords
        QE->>MeSH: Lookup MeSH terms
        MeSH-->>QE: Synonyms & descriptors
        QE-->>API: Expanded query

        API->>MV: Hybrid search (dense + BM25)
        MV-->>API: Top-K candidates

        API->>RR: Rerank candidates
        RR-->>API: Reranked results

        API-->>FE: SSE: citations event

        API->>LLM: Generate answer (query + abstracts)
        LLM-->>API: Answer tokens (streaming)
        API-->>FE: SSE: token events

        API->>GR: Validate output
        GR->>LLM: Grounding check
        LLM-->>GR: Issues (if any)
        GR->>MeSH: Terminology check
        MeSH-->>GR: Validation result
        GR-->>API: Warnings + disclaimer

        API-->>FE: SSE: done event
    end

    FE-->>User: Display answer + citations

    LLM--)LF: Auto-trace (tokens, latency, cost)

    Note over User,FE: Optional: Multi-Agent Analysis

    alt User triggers analysis
        User->>FE: Request analysis
        FE->>API: POST /analyze
        API->>LLM: 8 specialized agents (parallel)
        LLM-->>API: Agent results (JSON)
        API-->>FE: Agent analysis cards
        FE-->>User: Display agent insights
    end
